193→
194→  // --- Reset panel sizes on workspace switch ---
195→  // ResizablePanelGroup has no key prop — it stays mounted across workspace
196→  // switches so SimulatorPanel and BrowserPanel keep their native sessions alive.
197→  // Without the key, react-resizable-panels won't re-apply defaultSize on
198→  // re-render. We must imperatively collapse/expand panels to match the
